item.title: People who are willing to make me happy look here,Please!
item.dc:creator: @wayzey wayzey
item.description:
@wayzey wrote:

[quote=“Assassins Creed Fan, post:9, topic:279921”][quote author=wayzey link=topic=369371.msg2795904#msg2795904 date=1243072688]

Alright sorry but i still got the problem after animating that the model turns me invisible what were the reasons again??

Theres a number of possibilities.

  1. Your ints are invalid or you have none
  2. Your model contains faces or lines
    3. Your model is too high quality(don’t even consider this unless your model has over 1500 polys)
  3. You didn’t animate it right

Those are main reasons but there are many, many reasons for it going invisible.
[/quote]A RsPs client can hold 2000Poly Count.[/quote]

I knew it was somewhere around there so I just said don’t even consider that option unelss your model is over 1500 polys.
Offtopic: What’s the highest poly count a 503 server can support??
